version_description: Added ability to gather feedback from customers on how to improve the app further and serve their needs better

- Fix items sync issue
- Show error message if a pdf preview of an invoice could not be created
Fix configuration issues for new users
Added ability to gather feedback from customers on how to improve the app further and serve their needs better
Fixed photos sync problem which occurred to some users
Added ability to gather feedback from customers on how to improve the app further and serve their needs better
Fix custom currency and sync issues
Fix login issue on iOS 13 devices
